The '''[[World Polo Championship|World Polo Championship 2015]]''', tenth edition, took place in [[Santiago, Chile]] during March and April 2015 and was won by the host, beating the [[United States]] in the final.
This [[Sporting event|event]] will bring together six teams from around the world in the ''Club de Polo y Equitación San Cristóbal'' of the Chilean [[Capital city|capital]].
