'''Association Sportive Mangasport''' ('''AS Mangasport''') is a [[Gabon]]ese [[football (soccer)|football]] club based in [[Moanda]]. It was founded in 1962. They play at the [[Stade Henri Sylvoz]].

==Achievements==

*'''[[Gabon Championnat National D1]]: 9'''
:: 1995, 2000, 2004, 2005, 2006, 2008, 2014, 2015, 2018.

*'''[[Coupe du Gabon Interclubs]]: 6'''
:: 1964, 1994, 2001, 2005, 2007, 2011.

*'''[[Super Coupe du Gabon]]: 3'''
:: 1994, 2001, 2006.

==Performance in CAF competitions==
*'''[[CAF Champions League]]: 5 appearances'''
::[[CAF Champions League 2001|2001]]&nbsp;– Preliminary Round
::[[CAF Champions League 2005|2005]]&nbsp;– Preliminary Round
::[[CAF Champions League 2006|2006]]&nbsp;– Preliminary Round
::[[CAF Champions League 2007|2007]]&nbsp;– First Round
::[[CAF Champions League 2009|2009]]&nbsp;– First Round

*'''[[African Cup of Champions Clubs]]: 1 appearance'''
::[[African Cup of Champions Clubs 1996|1996]]&nbsp;– First Round

*'''[[CAF Confederation Cup]]: 1 appearance'''
::[[2012 CAF Confederation Cup|2012]]&nbsp;–

*'''[[CAF Cup]]: 1 appearance'''
::1997&nbsp;– First Round

*'''[[CAF Cup Winners' Cup]]: 2 appearances'''
::1995&nbsp;– First Round
::2002&nbsp;– Second Round

