The '''Carpathian Trophy''' ({{lang-ro|'Trofeul Carpaţi'}}) is an annual women's friendly [[team handball|handball]] tournament organised by the [[Romanian Handball Federation]]. The first edition took place in [[Bucharest]] in 1959.

== Tournament structure ==
It reached the 50th edition in November 2018. There is no precise format for the tournament, even though recently there were four participating teams.

