'''FC Belize''' is a [[Belize]]an [[football (soccer)|football]] team which currently competes in the [[Premier League of Belize]] (PLB) of the [[Football Federation of Belize]].

The team is based in [[Belize City]].  Their home stadium is [[MCC Grounds (stadium)|MCC Grounds]].

