The '''Quai 54''' is the only streetball tournament worldwide sponsored by [[Jordan Brand]]. Founded by [[Hammadoun Sidibe]], it has historically been held the last weekend of June every summer in [[Paris]] since 2002.

20,000 fans are granted free entry and watch the two-day basketball tournament, including  a slam dunk contest.<ref>http://www.frenchtodeath.com/quai-54-2015/</ref>

The venue each year is the Place de la Concorde, Paris which is very close to the Eiffel Tower in the city's eighth arrondissement.

